'''Gunnar''' came to the ER with the Keller family. He was at their family reunion despite not being related to them.

==History==
Gunnar was at a Keller family reunion despite not being related to the family. While playing tug-o-war, four members of the family were injured. Gunnar went to the ER along with the rest of the family. There, [[Cash Keller|Cash]] tried to blame Gunnar for the injuries, because of Gunnar's large size, but [[Tony Keller|Tony]] told him that [[Al Keller|Al]] was really at fault because he's the one who suggested they play.

==Relationships==
===Friendships===
He is friends with [[Tony Keller]], which is how he ended up at a Keller family reunion.
